des:
Amtrak Train Status lets you check the arrival or departure status of active trains up to 10 hours prior to departure. 

- To start a conversation, say “Alexa, launch Amtrak.”
- Ask for arrival or departure information.
- Include a train number and station or city name in your question.
- Check status for today or tomorrow.

Remember that late trains can make up time between stations, so plan accordingly.
